    "secondary": "Investigation efficiency enhancement reduces resolution timeframe through digital platform implementation and gap elimination. Complete digital custody logging eliminates manual paper record searching. Individual-level authentication replaces crew or department-level tracking. Automated custody chain reconstruction provides instant timeline visibility. Mobile documentation capabilities ensure all custody transfers receive recording. Training reinforcement emphasizes documentation discipline. Compliance monitoring identifies persistent gaps requiring intervention. Simplified workflows encourage voluntary compliance through convenience. Progressive automation adds photographic evidence and condition documentation strengthening investigation capability."
