    "secondary": "Investigation enhancement implements individual-level tracking replacing department or shift-level granularity. User authentication requirements ensure specific person identification at every custody transfer. Digital platform implementation mandates individual login or badge scan. Simplified mobile workflows encourage personal rather than group checkout. Access control enforcement prevents equipment removal without individual documentation. Training programs establish personal accountability expectations. Compliance monitoring identifies persistent group-level tracking requiring intervention. Pattern analysis becomes feasible at individual level enabling targeted corrective action. Cost recovery workflows enable individual billing for damages rather than department-wide charges."
